{"id":330346,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/萝卜网-我当年整过人，我今天道歉了！/","date":"2014-01-19T18:38:20Z","modified":"2014-01-19T18:38:20Z","title":"萝卜网 | 我当年整过人，我今天道歉了！","content":"<p>@胡释之 ：原社科院副院长刘吉回忆当年在清华大学作为新党员参与反右，后悔不已，当场向当年受害的右派同学道歉。全场掌声响起。</p>\n<p>刘吉说，文革中自己受批判时才体会到自己反右时的错，激动地说，现在有人要为文革翻案，可我们这些经历过文革的人还没死啊！</p>\n<p>刘吉最后说，我当年整过人，我今天道歉了！年轻人以后再也不要整人了！如果有人要整你们，你们要反抗！<strong>如果有人要再搞文革，你们要打倒他！</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/68f0330822e322f0419330af46e2b83e.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-330353\" alt=\"68f0330822e322f0419330af46e2b83e\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/68f0330822e322f0419330af46e2b83e.jpg\" width=\"478\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/68f0330822e322f0419330af46e2b83e.jpg 478w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/68f0330822e322f0419330af46e2b83e-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" /></a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&amp;id=b4fd4ae247\" method=\"POST\"><a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a></p>\n<p><input id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" style=\"display: block;\" type=\"email\" name=\"EMAIL\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required=\"\" size=\"25\" value=\"\" /><br />\n<input id=\"in_post_subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" type=\"submit\" name=\"subscribe\" value=\"点击订阅\" /></p>\n</form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,20534],"tags":[20239,24481]}